INSTRUCTION FOR USING THE INTERFACE:
1)Welcome Screen Brief greeting → Auto-closes in 3 seconds.
2)Login Enter: sta001 / givemethekeys123 → Click Login.
3)Booking Area Fill required fields (Name, Age ≥18, Days 1-28) → Select car/fuel type → Add extras.
4)Summary Confirm details → Click Confirm to save.
